0tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217e39d6c-1ad7-4fd5-b652-e3016598f9fa%5C%22%3E'An%20airbrushed%20look%20and%20lustre'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20checking%20with%20dermatologists%20that%20microtox%20is%20safe%2C%20I%20quickly%20realized%20this%20relatively%20new%20treatment%20isn't%20offered%20by%20many%20clinics%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20I%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20a%20consultation%20with%20the%20Taktouk%20Clinic%20in%20London's%20ultra-affluent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-property-london-rutland-gate-tour-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKnightsbridge%20neighborhood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20three%20years%20ago%20became%20one%20of%20the%20first%20places%20in%20the%20UK%20to%20offer%20microtox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20treatment%20was%20originally%20%C2%A3695%20(%24922)%2C%20but%20the%20clinic%20told%20me%20the%20price%20was%20lowered%20to%20%C2%A3495%20(%24657)%20in%20July%20to%20bring%20it%20in%20line%20with%20their%20other%20skin%20boosters.%20Business%20Insider%20was%20given%20a%20media%20rate%20of%20%C2%A3476%20(%24631).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Christine%20Hall%2C%20an%20aesthetic%20doctor%20at%20the%20clinic%2C%20and%20I%20talked%20on%20Zoom%20about%20my%20skin%20and%20what%20the%20treatment%20involved.%20She%20told%20me%20not%20to%20drink%20any%20alcohol%2024%20hours%20before%20or%20after%20microtox%2C%20and%20also%20to%20avoid%20painkillers%2C%20the%20sauna%2C%20steam%20room%2C%20and%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christine%20Hall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675aff65dc8b666017f2aac4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Christine%20Hall%20of%20the%20Taktouk%20Clinic%20first%20heard%20about%20microtox%20being%20used%20in%20South%20Korea.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blackett%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20said%20microtox%20is%20incre