oom%2C%20complete%20with%20expensive%20perfumes%2C%20to%20cleanse%20my%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20greeted%20me%20in%20the%20waiting%20room%2C%20and%20I%20was%20reassured%20that%20her%20glowing%2C%20smooth%20complexion%20was%20neither%20frozen%20nor%20line-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20assessed%20my%20skin%20and%20said%20it%20was%20in%20good%20condition%2C%20meaning%20microtox%20wouldn't%20have%20a%20hugely%20noticeable%20effect%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20popular%20with%20people%20who%20have%20very%20oily%20skin%20or%20want%20to%20minimize%20redness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel's%20face%20covered%20in%20a%20numbing%20cream%20and%20sheet%20mask.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad72b91c1cc343d47fb26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel's%20face%20covered%20in%20numbing%20cream%20and%20a%20sheet%20mask.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blackett%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClinic%20manager%20Hilda%20Akpenyi%20then%20applied%20a%20powerful%20numbing%20cream%20to%20my%20face%2C%20topped%20with%20a%20plastic%20mask%20to%20stop%20it%20from%20evaporating.%20The%20cream%20took%20half%20an%20hour%20to%20take%20full%20effect%2C%20and%20my%20face%20quickly%20started%20to%20tingle%20and%20feel%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20explained%20that%2C%20unlike%20other%20clinics%2C%20Taktouk%20dilutes%20Botox%20with%20Klardie%20Cellup%20Ruby%20Solution%2C%20which%20she%20said%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-skin-flooding-tiktok-trend-hyaluronic-acid-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehyaluronic%20acid%3C%2Fa%3E%20skin%20booster%20designed%20to%20reduce%20pigmentation%2C%20hydrate%2C%20and%20boost%20radiance.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20makes%20Taktouk's%20treatment%20around%20%C2%A3100%20(%24132)%20more%20expensive%20than%20its%20competitors%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efdc8c58-564f-410d-b5fd-894f16dae208%5C%22%3EMicrotox%20is%20a%20bearable%2C%2020-minute%20procedure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20took%20me%20to%20a%20spacious%20and%20bright%20treatment%20room%2C%20where%20she%20wiped%20off%20the%20numbing%20cream%20and%20cleansed%20my%20face%20again%20before%20I%20made%20myself%20comfortable%20in%20a%20reclining%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20needle%2C%20Botox%2C%20and%20Klardie%20Cellup%20Ruby%20Solution%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad84f52dd0818d1a6930e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBotox%20and%20Klardie%20Cellup%20Ruby%20Solution%20are%20combined%20for%20microtox%20procedures%20at%20the%20Taktouk%20Clinic.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blackett%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2020%20minutes%2C%20Hall%20made%20around%20100%20injections%20about%20one%20millimeter%20deep%20across%20the%20entirety%20of%20my%20face%2C%20unlike%20Botox%20which%20targets%20specific%20areas.%20She%20regularly%20changed%20the%20needle%20to%20keep%20it%20sharp%20and%20avoided%20going%20too%20close%20to%20the%20muscles%20of%20the%20mouth%20and%20eyes%20to%20prevent%20drooping%2C%20which%20can%20happen%20if%20it%20goes%20in%20too%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20slightly%20painful%20but%20bearable%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20just%20as%20you'd%20imagine%20lots%20of%20tiny%20needle%20pricks%20would.%20Having%20a%20numb%20face%20was%20arguably%20more%20uncomfortable.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20able%20to%20chat%20throughout%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20reassured%20hearing%20Hall's%20approach%20is%20all%20about%20small%2C%20subtle%2C%20natural-looking%20tweaks.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ethos%20of%20the%20clinic%20is%20that%20we're%20extremely%20conservative%20and%20we're%20very%20happy%20to%20say%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20finished%20by%20applying%20a%20soothing%20moisturizer%20to%20my%20skin.%20What%20I%20didn't%20realize%20until%20she%20held%20up%20a%20mirror%20was%20that%20my%20face%20was%20covered%20in%20bumps%20from%20each%20needle%20prick.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstruggled-with-severe-acne-got-rid-of-it-with-accutane-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20acne%20I%20used%20to%20have%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20ironic.%20Hall%20said%20the%20bumps%20would%20ease%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Hosie%20reclining%20while%20being%20administered%20microtox%20by%20Christine%20hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad7b491c1cc343d47fb31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223939%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20having%20microtox.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blackett%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20traveled%20across%20London%20to%20meet%20a%20friend%2C%20I%20was%20conscious%20of%20the%20looks%20I%20was%20getting.%20It%20took%20more%20than%20a%20few%20hours%20for%20the%20bumps%20to%20reduce%2C%20but%2015%20hours%20later%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20they%20were%2095%25%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1d8384d-af76-487f-9cea-bd8410de2d71%5C%22%3EMicrotox%20made%20my%20skin%20glow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20said%20that%20the%20effects%20of%20microtox%20could%20appear%20within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20and%20would%20peak%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20fortnight%2C%20I%20dutifully%20monitored%20my%20face%2C%20conscious%20of%20every%20pore%20and%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20thought%20my%20skin%20appeared%20slightly%20smoother%2C%20with%20more%20sheen.%20As%20the%20days%20passed%2C%20my%20complexion%20looked%20somewhat%20tighter%20and%20glowier%20without%20being%20shiny%2C%20despite%20the%20lines%20on%20my%20face%20looking%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20disappointed%20that%20my%20freckles%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20weeks%2C%20my%20skin%20looked%20smoother%20and%20younger%20overall%2C%20and%20my%20crow's%20feet%20diminished.%20I%20was%20starting%20to%20understand%20why%20microtox%20is%20called%20%26quot%3Bglass%20skin%26quot%3B%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Rachel%20Hosie's%20face%20before%20and%20after%20microtox.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad8a252dd0818d1a69316%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel's%20face%20before%20microtox%20(left)%20and%20two%20weeks%20after.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20effect%20was%20slight%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20knew%20I'd%20had%20the%20treatment%20told%20me%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%26quot%3B%20see%20a%20difference%2C%20otherwise%20no%20one%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20is%20meant%20to%20last%20two%20to%20three%20months%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20negligible.%20My%20skin%20gradually%20went%20back%20to%20normal%20over%20the%20weeks%2C%20so%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20tell%20when%20the%20results%20wore%20off.%20It%20was%20like%20I'd%20had%20a%20really%20good%20facial%2C%20with%20longer-lasting%20results%20but%20a%20significantly%20higher%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22460fe23c-acda-409b-9486-927be8bfe62e%5C%22%3EThe%20result%20didn't%20justify%20the%20cost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20facial%20tweakments%20is%20paradoxical.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20want%20subtle%20changes%20so%20people%20can't%20tell%20you've%20had%20anything%20done.%20But%20on%20the%20other%2C%20you%20want%20enough%20of%20an%20effect%20to%20justify%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Hosie%20raising%20her%20eyebrows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ad9bd91c1cc343d47fb50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20could%20still%20mover%20her%20face%20after%20having%20microtox.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20microtox%20wasn't%20worth%20the%20cost%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20the%20prime%20candidate%2C%20and%20people%20who%20have%20oily%20skin%20and%20large%20pores%20might%20have%20better%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20money%20were%20no%20object%2C%20I%20might%20have%20had%20microtox%20again%2C%20considering%20it%20an%20expensive%20(and%20less%20relaxing)%20facial%20that%20would%20turn%20back%20the%20clock%20on%20my%20face%20a%20year%20or%20two%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20anti-aging%20holy%20grail%20of%20having%20smoothed%20wrinkles%20while%20maintaining%20facial%20expressions%20remains%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrotox-review-botox-antiaging-treatment-smoothes-wrinkles-lines-freezing-face-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734169261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c4997cf8d1359a2dfcb89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrotox-review-botox-antiaging-treatment-smoothes-wrinkles-lines-freezing-face-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20look%20on%20trend%2C%20microtox%20sounded%20like%20a%20soft-landing%20into%20injectable%20cosmetic%20treatments.%20It%20made%20my%20skin%20glow%2C%20but%20wasn't%20noticeable%20enough.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrotox-review-botox-antiaging-treatment-smoothes-wrinkles-lines-freezing-face-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2