0Jaffray%20Woodriff%20stands%20outside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c6819cf8d1359a2dfe48c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaffray%20Woodriff%20is%20excited%20about%20what's%20next%20for%20QIM.%3Cp%3EQIM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJaffray%20Woodriff's%20Quantitative%20Investment%20Management%20wants%20to%20grow%20after%20a%20stretch%20of%20tough%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2021-year-old%20manager%20changed%20its%20research%20process%2C%20freeing%20Woodriff%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20he%20does%20best.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20conversations%20with%20Woodriff%20and%20those%20running%20the%20%241.1%20billion%20firm%2C%20they're%20as%20optimistic%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJaffray%20Woodriff%2C%20the%20face%20of%20%241.1%20billion%20Quantitative%20Investment%20Management%2C%20is%20stepping%20back%20into%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%2C%20which%20fell%20from%20%245%20billion%20in%20assets%20a%20decade%20ago%20thanks%20to%20a%20stretch%20of%20underperformance%2C%20has%20been%20quiet%E2%80%94likely%20too%20quiet.%20When%20contacted%20for%20this%20story%2C%20a%20few%20allocators%20who%20had%20met%20with%20the%20firm%20before%20but%20hadn't%20been%20in%20touch%20for%20a%20number%20of%20years%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethought%20it%20had%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20family%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadquartered%20in%20Charlottesville%2C%20the%20western%20Virginia%20town%20home%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%2C%20QIM%20became%20an%20easy%20option%20to%20skip%20for%20investors%20looking%20to%20meet%20with%20multiple%20funds%20in%20a%20day%20in%20places%20like%20New%20York%20or%20Greenwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20its%20three%20cofounders%20%E2%80%94%2055-year-old%20Woodriff%2C%20president%20Mike%20Geismar%2C%20and%20researcher%20Greyson%20Williams%20%E2%80%94%20are%20as%20optimistic%20as%20ever%20about%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20as%20excited%20as%20I've%20ever%20seen%20him%20about%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Geismar%2C%20who%20was%20roommates%20with%20Woodriff%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20nearly%20a%20decade%20before%20QIM%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20going%20to%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20hires%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20research%20team%20have%20freed%20Woodriff%2C%20still%20the%20firm's%20investment%20engine%2C%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20idea%20generation%20and%20less%20on%20implementation.%20There's%20a%20renewed%20focus%20on%20marketing%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20is%20courting%20investors%20from%20institutions%20around%20the%20world%20with%20hopes%20of%20growing%20up%20to%20%244%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20the%20time%20is%20right%20for%20firms%20like%20QIM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20large%20multistrategy%20managers%20like%20Millennium%20and%20its%20peers%20become%20a%20bigger%20part%20of%20institutions'%20portfolios%2C%20there's%20a%20growing%20need%20for%20volatility%20that%20a%20place%20like%20QIM%2C%20which%20systematically%20trades%20equities%2C%20indices%2C%20futures%2C%20and%20more%20and%20has%20no%20correlation%20to%20stock%20or%20bond%20markets%2C%20can%20provide.%20Performance%20ticking%20up%20has%20also%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%20returns%20from%20both%20programs%2C%20including%20a%2019.2%25%20gain%20in%20its%20oldest%20strategy%2C%20in%202022%20opened%20eyes%20again.%20This%20year%2C%20through%20October%2C%20the%20firm's%20more%20aggressive%20offering%20is%20up%20more%20than%2034%25%2C%20while%20its%20older%20program%20has%20returned%201.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20math%20geeks.%20That's%20what%20Jaffray%20is%2C%20and%20his%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Salem%20Abraham%2C%20an%20investor%20in%20the%20firm%20for%2017%20years%20and%20a%20longtime%20business%20partner%20of%20late%20billionaire%20T.%20Boone%20Pickens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQIM%20is%20the%20type%20of%20firm%20Harry%20Markowitz%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20to%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abraham%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20late%20academic%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20Modern%20Portfolio%20Theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204d5504f-d690-4676-904f-7e44643b0358%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVolatile%20ride%20for%20a%20volatile%20manager%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20quant%20manager%20was%20a%20darling%20in%20the%20industry%20at%20its%20start.%20Woodriff%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Charlottesville%20and%20owns%20a%20farm%20nearby%2C%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20farm%20outside%20the%20%26quot%3Bmagical%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20went%20to%20college%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%2C%20where%20he%20came%20up%20with%20the%20foundation%20of%20his%20trading%20system%20during%20a%20Pepsi-fueled%2C%2040-hour%20coding%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20made%20history%20by%20making%20the%20largest%20donation%20in%20the%20school's%20history%2C%20%24120%20million%2C%20to%20create%20a%20school%20of%20data%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodriff%2C%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20monk%20in%20managed%20futures%26quot%3B%20by%20a%202009%20Institutional%20Investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.institutionalinvestor.com%2Farticle%2F2btfxvo24pejsjnep4dts%2Fpremium%2Fqims-jaffray-woodriff-the-monk-in-managed-futures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20got%20the%20reputation%20of%20someone%20%26quot%3Bobsessed%20with%20markets%20and%20how%20they%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kyle%20Dunn%2C%20a%20former%20hedge-fund%20marketer%20who%20now%20consults%20for%20funds%20and%20worked%20with%20QIM%20to%20develop%20their%20%26quot%3Bstory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20Global%20Program%20strategy%20soared%20in%20its%20first%20two%20full%20years%20of%20trading%20in%202004%20and%202005%2C%20with%20gains%20of%2021.8%25%20and%2018.4%25%2C%20before%20its%20strong%20crisis%20showing%20put%20the%20firm%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20bigger%20allocators.%20With%20gains%20of%2029.6%25%20in%202007%20and%2012.5%25%20in%202008%2C%20the%20firm%20added%20assets%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%202010s%20were%20not%20a%20decade%20for%20a%20strategy%20uncorrelated%20to%20stocks.%20The%20firm's%20Global%20Program%20lost%20money%20in%202013%2C%202014%2C%202018%2C%20and%202019.%20QIM's%20Tactical%20Aggressive%20strategy%2C%20launched%20in%202008%20and%20willing%20to%20take%20bigger%20swings%20than%20the%20flagship%2C%20followed%20a%2060%25%20gain%20in%202017%20with%20a%2042%25%20drop%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssets%20left%20for%20more%20stable%20managers%20with%20strategies%20that%20weren't%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20lots%20of%20conversations%20with%20clients%20about%20what%20went%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Geismar%2C%20QIM's%20president.%20There%20were%20also%20conversations%20internally%20about%20how%20it%20had%20gotten%20to%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodriff%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bthought%20experiments%26quot%3B%20about%20going%20the%20family-office%20route%20or%20closing%20one%20of%20the%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consistent%20theme%20has%20been%3A%20The%20research%20looks%20way%20too%20good%20to%20give%20up%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20the%20tough%20stretch%20of%20performance%20in%20the%20mid-2010s.%20The%20firm%20was%20helped%20by%20its%20equity%20investment%20into%20Florida-based%20Voloridge%2C%20a%20%249%20billion%20quant%20manager%20run%20by%20David%20Vogel%2C%20who%20first%20met%20Woodriff%20when%20they%20were%20competing%20in%20a%20Netflix%20data%20science%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQIM%20charges%20no%20management%20fee%2C%20so%20when%20the%20firm's%20strategies%20lost%20money%2C%20there%20were%20no%20revenues%20coming%20in.%20But%20thanks%20to%20Voloridge's%20rapid%20growth%20and%20strong%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firm%20went%20from%20less%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%202010%20to%20more%20than%20%246%20billion%20in%202020%20%E2%80%94%20bonuses%20were%20able%20to%20still%20be%20paid%20out%20to%20keep%20employees%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Woodriff%20admitted%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bgotten%20close%20to%20the%20threshold%20of%20shutting%20things%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d47b2dcb-f7c5-47ae-b8e9-783a638b63cb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20being%20an%20idea%20guy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20manager%20reworked%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20risk%20management%20was%20overhauled%2C%20and%20Woodriff%20began%20sharing%20some%20of%20the%20research%20responsibilities%2C%20in%20part%20thanks%20to%20the%202022%20hiring%20of%20Chris%20Lankford%2C%20one%20of%20five%20research%20team%20members%20with%20Woodriff%20and%20Williams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELankford%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20as%20a%20consultant%20for%20QIM%20for%20a%20year%20before%20joining%20the%20firm%20full-time%2C%20has%20a%20doctorate%20in%20systems%20engineering%20(from%20UVA%2C%20naturally)%20and%20previously%20cofounded%20a%20company%20that%20tracks%20the%20eye%20movements%20of%20disabled%20individuals%20to%20help%20them%20communicate.%20The%20company%20was%20sold%20to%20DynaVox%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20career%2C%20I%20had%20people%20who%20could%20listen%20to%20me%20describe%20a%20complicated%20scenario%20and%20process%20and%20go%20do%20it%20three%20times%20faster%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodriff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20such%20an%20increased%20speed%20in%20trying%20out%20ideas.%20It's%20a%20shame%20we%20didn't%20have%20this%20dynamic%20five%2C%2010%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20given%20some%20relief%20to%20allocators%20who%20were%20concerned%20with%20all%20of%20the%20risk-taking%20being%20tied%20to%20one%20person.%20Woodriff%20said%20there%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20consistent%20drumbeat%20from%20investors%20and%20potential%20investors%20asking%20how%20dare%20you%20be%20the%20only%20one%20working%20on%20alpha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20been%20a%20difficult%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20part%20because%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20have%20known%20my%20best%20skill%20is%20idea%20generation%20and%20creativity%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20time%20to%20devote%20all%20of%20his%20energy%20toward%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodruff%20said%20the%20research%20team%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20longtime%20data%20scientist%20Seth%20Oldham%20and%2017-year%20QIM%20vet%20Greg%20Tylka%2C%20gives%20him%20a%20better%20answer%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bbus%20question%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20as%20in%2C%20who%20would%20take%20over%20if%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20bus%2C%20a%20common%20question%20allocators%20ask%20during%20due%20diligence%20to%20understand%20succession%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELankford%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20given%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20been%20a%20great%20link%26quot%3B%20between%20Woodriff%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20business%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Jaffray%20appreciated%20the%20constraints%20on%20his%20time%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a804a921-4b02-4cce-a63f-44ca1fee099f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20going%20anywhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Woodriff%20has%20passions%20outside%20work%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20his%20work%20building%20out%20the%20UVA's%20newest%20school%2C%20he%20received%20a%20US%20Squash%20Special%20Recognition%20Award%20in%202014%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bleadership%20and%20substantial%20contributions%20to%20squash%2C%26quot%3B%20of%20which%20he's%20an%20avid%20player%20%E2%80%94%20one%20conversation%20with%20the%20intense%20researcher%20reveals%20where%20his%20true%20passion%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20in%20college%20I'd%20never%20want%20to%20retire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20nothing%20about%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20has%20changed%20that%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodriff%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbored%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20retired%2C%20his%20cofounder%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20passion%2C%20career%2C%20and%20hobby%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20close%20to%20him%20say%20his%20renewed%20interest%20in%20the%20firm's%20strategies%20and%20more%20time%20to%20think%20have%20not%20so%20much%20reignited%20his%20passion%20as%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20a%20unique%20find%20and%20a%20unique%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abraham%2C%20the%20investor%20in%20the%20firm%20and%20a%20longtime%20quantitative%20trader%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20things%20to%20make%20the%20stew%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Stocks%20and%20bonds%20are%20the%20meat%20and%20potatoes%20of%20a%20portfolio.%20Funds%20like%20QIM%20are%20the%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20spicy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20college%2C%20Woodriff%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20totally%20different%20from%20everyone%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20regard%2C%20it%20should%20be%20no%20surprise%20the%20firm%20didn't%20shutter%20during%20its%20tough%20years%20or%20that%20Woodriff%20still%20believes%20in%20what%20he%20and%20his%20team%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20feel%20like%20I'm%20very%20good%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjaffray-woodriff-quantitative-investment-management-strategy-quant-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734167702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c6ad952dd0818d1a713eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originI