20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGukesh%20was%20not%20playing%20aggressive%20or%20anything.%20He%20had%20an%20extra%20pawn%20and%20was%20circling%20around%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20way%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20Anand%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tactic%20of%20wearing%20down%20the%20opponent%2C%20even%20when%20it%20looked%20as%20good%20as%20a%20stalemate%2C%20proved%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDing%20unexpectedly%20relaxed%20for%20one%20moment.%20These%20moments%20are%20very%20common%20in%20World%20Championship%20matches%2C%20almost%20in%20every%20match%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Anand%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20Gukesh's%20transformation%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%20at%20his%20WestBridge%20Anand%20Chess%20Academy%20(WACA)%2C%20the%20legend%20said%20it%20was%20a%20source%20of%20immense%20pride%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20watch%20his%20meteoric%20journey%20through%20the%20cycle%20to%20the%20World%20Championship%20match.%20It's%20a%20golden%20generation%20of%20Indian%20players%20establishing%20themselves%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Gukesh%20to%20become%20the%20youngest%20world%20champion%20in%20history%20is%20truly%20special.%20It's%20definitely%20a%20very%20talented%20golden%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734166620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F82fkn5no_d-gukesh-afp_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fviswanathan-anand-responds-as-ex-world-champion-criticises-d-gukeshs-title-triumph-7239007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20world%20champion%20Vladimir%20Kramnik%20was%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20quality%20of%20ch