hip%20was%20serious%2C%20involving%20frequent%20visits%20to%20hotels%20and%20shared%20stays%20at%20Avnish's%20residence%20in%20Katihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20promised%20to%20marry%20me%20and%20start%20a%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Gunjan%20alleged.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20also%20taken%20me%20to%20his%20school.%20We%20were%20in%20love%20for%20four%20years.%20But%20when%20I%20informed%20my%20family%20about%20it%2C%20and%20we%20approached%20him%20for%20marriage%2C%20he%20refused.%20This%20was%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20Gunjan's%20family%20discovered%20the%20couple%20together%20in%20Katihar.%20They%20allegedly%20kidnapped%20Avnish%20and%20forcibly%20married%20him%20in%20a%20temple.%20A%20viral%20video%20shows%20Avnish%20being%20held%20by%20several%20men%20while%20Gunjan%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20wedding%20saree%20and%20vermilion%20on%20her%20head%2C%20stands%20nearby.%20Avnish%20is%20visibly%20distressed%20as%20he%20is%20coerced%20into%20completing%20marriage%20rituals%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20forced%20ceremony%2C%20Gunjan%20accompanied%20her%20family%20to%20Avnish's%20home%20in%20Rajaura%2C%20but%20chaos%20ensued.%20Avnish%20reportedly%20managed%20to%20escape.%20When%20Gunjan%20eventually%20arrived%20at%20the%20house%2C%20Avnish's%20family%20refused%20to%20accept%20her%20as%20part%20of%20their%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGunjan%20has%20since%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%2C%20pleading%20for%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvnish%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20all%20allegations%20of%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20love%20for%20that%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%20%26quot%3BShe%20harassed%20me%20by%20repeatedly%20calling%20and%20stalking%20me.%20On%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20some%20men%20kidnapped%20me%20in%20a%20Scorpio%20vehicle%20while%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way%20to%20school.%20They%20beat%20me%2C%20forcibly%20applied%20vermilion%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20perform%20rituals.%20I%20protested%20throughout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvnish%20has%20also%20filed%20a%20complaint%2C%20alleging%20kidnapping%20and%20physical%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734166260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9ccsh1n8_bihar-forced-wedding-_625x300_14_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-teacher-kidnapped-on-way-to-school-forced-to-marry-woman-at-gunpoint-7246439%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Avnish%20Kumar%20had%20recently%20cleared%20the%20Bihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20exam%20to%20become%20a%20teacher.%20On%20Friday%2C%20he%20was%20kidnapped%2C%20beaten%20and%20then%20forced%20to%20marry%20a%20woman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korean%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20Impeached%20Over%20Failed%20Martial%20Law%20Bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20lawmakers%20impeach%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20over%20martial%20law%20bid%2C%20suspending%20him%20from%20office%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%20caused%20mass%20outrage%20and%20resulted%20in%20constitutional%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20voted%20on%20a%20motion%20to%20impeach%C2%A0President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%2C%20as%20a%20parliament%20livestream%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E204%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20300-member%20house%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20motion%2C%20while%2085%20voted%20against.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20constitution%2C%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%20Han%20Duck-soo%20will%20be%20the%20interim%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20now%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20on%20whether%20to%20reinstate%20or%20remove%20him.%20This%20could%20take%20up%20to%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%203rd%2C%20when%20the%20martial%20law%20was%20declared%20by%C2%A0President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%2C%20soldiers%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20National%20Assembly%20and%20the%20officer%20who%20led%20the%20soldiers%20said%20that%20they%20were%20ordered%20to%20forcibly%20remove%20lawmakers%20so%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20150%20votes%20they%20needed%20to%20overturn%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20had%20declared%20martial%20law%20accusing%20the%20opposition%20of%20paralysing%20the%20government.%20However%2C%20the%20declaration%20was%20voted%20down%20and%20the%20law%20rescinded%20within%20hours%20of%20its%20imposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Saturday%2C%20Yoon%20survived%20an%20impeachment%20motion%20after%20People%20Power%20Party%20lawmakers%20boycotted%20a%20floor%20vote%20but%20on%20Saturday%20some%20members%20of%20his%20own%20party%20helped%20pass%20the%20motion%20to%20impeach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20not%20been%20any%20immediate%20reaction%20from%20the%20Yoon%2C%20though%20he%20was%20watching%20the%20vote%20from%20his%20residence%20in%20Seoul%20as%20per%20KBS%2C%20the%20national%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPark%20Chan-dae%2C%20the%20floor%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20South%20Korean%20people%20and%20for%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20also%20faces%20criminal%20investigations%20because%20of%20his%20decision%20to%20impose%20the%20martial%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734166260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8a858gf8_south-korea-impeachment-reuters_625x300_14_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korean-lawmakers-impeach-president-yoon-suk-yeol-over-martial-law-bid-7246286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawmakers%20voted%20on%20a%20motion%20t