ep%204%3A%20Once%20you%20land%20on%20the%20'Update%20Aadhaar%20Details%20(Online)'%20page%2C%20click%20on%20'Document%20Update'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%205%3A%20Enter%20your%2012-digit%20Aadhaar%20Card%20number%2C%20captcha%20code%20and%20then%20click%20on%20'Send%20OTP'.%20This%20will%20send%20an%20OTP%20to%20your%20registered%20mobile%20number.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%206%3A%20Enter%20the%20OTP%20received%20on%20your%20phone%20and%20proceed%20with%20the%20details%20you%20wish%20to%20update%2C%20like%20name%2C%20address%20or%20date%20of%20birth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%207%3A%20Once%20you%20are%20done%20with%20the%20update%2C%20you%20will%20be%20required%20to%20upload%20relevant%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%208%3A%20Check%20all%20the%20details%20before%20submitting%20your%20request.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20then%20receive%20an%20Update%20Request%20Number%20(URN)%20on%20your%20mobile%20phone%20to%20track%20the%20status%20of%20your%20Aadhaar%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20must%20ensure%20that%20date%20of%20birth%2Fgender%20updates%20are%20limited%20to%20one-time%20changes.%20To%20change%20your%20biometric%20details%20(fingerprints%2C%20iris%20scans%2C%20or%20image)%2C%20you%20have%20to%20visit%20an%20Aadhaar%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20update%20Aadhaar%20offline%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%201%3A%20Download%20the%20Aadhaar%20Enrolment%20Form%20from%20the%20official%20UIDAI%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%202%3A%20Fill%20out%20the%20details%20and%20visit%20a%20nearby%20Aadhaar%20centre.%20Take%20the%20necessary%20documents%20along%20with%20your%20filled%20form%20and%20necessary%20documents%20to%20the%20Aadhaar%20Enrolment%20Centre%20or%20Aadhaar%20Sewa%20Kendra.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStep%203%3A%20You%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20provide%20your%20biometric%20data.%20After%20that%2C%20you%20receive%20an%20acknowledgement%20slip%20with%20a%20URN%20to%20track%20t