ets%2C%20Bullets%20Every%20Day%26quot%3B%3A%20Indian%20Rescued%20From%20Syria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20Indians%20evacuated%20from%20Syria%20arrived%20at%20Delhi%20airport.%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20expressed%20happiness%20on%20reaching%20India%20and%20praised%20Indian%20embassy%20for%20their%20efforts%20in%20bringing%20them%20back%20home.%20This%20action%20of%20the%20embassy%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20India's%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20protect%20its%20citizens%20caught%20in%20the%20violence%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20reaching%20Delhi%20airport%2C%20the%20Indian%20national%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20there%2015-20%20days%20ago.%20We%20did%20not%20know%20this%20would%20happen.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20evacuated%20us.%20First%20we%20they%20took%20us%20to%20Lebanon%20and%20then%20Goa%20and%20today%20we%20have%20reached%20Delhi.%20We%20are%20happy%20that%20we%20have%20reached%20our%20country.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20helped%20us%20a%20lot.%20They%20brought%20us%20in%20a%20bus%20from%20Syria%20to%20Lebanon%20as%20flights%20are%20not%20operating%20in%20Syria.%20Then%2C%20they%20brought%20us%20to%20Goa%20in%20a%20flight%20and%20then%20they%20brought%20us%20to%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Indian%20national%20said%20that%20the%20embassy%20told%20them%20to%20reach%20Damascus%20and%20then%20they%20were%20taken%20to%20Beirut%20safe%20zone.%20He%20stressed%20that%20the%20situation%20there%20was%20very%20critical%20and%20that%20every%20day%20they%20had%20heard%20the%20sounds%20of%20rockets%20and%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20national%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20doing%20job%20in%20Syria%20for%20the%20past%20four%20months.%20One%20day%2C%20while%20working%20at%20the%20plant%2C%20we%20saw%20two-three%20rockets.%20We%20informed%20the%20embassy%20and%20they%20told%20us%20to%20come%20to%20Damascus.%20We%20stayed%20there%20for%201-2%20days%2C%20then%20we%20were%20taken%20to%20Beirut%20safe%20zone.%20There%20was%20some%20issue%20with%20the%20ticket%20there%20for%20two%20days.%20After%20two%20days%2C%20our%20ticket%20was%20booked%20from%20Beirut%20to%20Doha.%20Then%2C%20our%20ticket%20was%20booked%20from%20Doha%20to%20Qatar%20and%20Doha%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20situation%20there%20is%20very%20critical.%20Every%20day%20we%20heard%20the%20sounds%20of%20rockets%20and%20bullets.%20The%20embassy%20helped%20us%20a%20lot%20and%20provided%20all%20the%20facilities%20including%20food%2C%20good%20accommodation.%20They%20even%20booked%20tickets%20for%20us.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20embassy%20and%20Indian%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20national%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20thank%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20Indian%20Embassy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Indian%20national%20thanked%20the%20government%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20their%20support.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20Indian%20embassy%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20their%20support.%20The%20condition%20there%20is%20very%20bad.%20We%20got%20scared%20there%20as%20we%20heard%20the%20sounds%20of%20rockets%20and%20bullets%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20be%20back%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20gratitude%20to%20PM%20Modi%20for%20bringing%20them%20back%20home%2C%20another%20Indian%20national%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20embassy.%20They%20told%20us%20to%20leave%20Syria.%20We%20also%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20bomb%20blasts.%20The%20situation%20there%20was%20very%20serious.%20The%20embassy%20called%20us%20and%20shifted%20us%20to%20Beirut%2C%20and%20then%20after%20two%20or%20three%20days%2C%20we%20were%20brought%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20We%20are%20grateful%20to%20PM%20Modi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20that%2077%20Indian%20nationals%20had%20been%20evacuated%20from%20strife-torn%20Syria%20so%20far.%20The%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20embassies%20in%20Middle%20East%20region%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20Indians%20there%20and%20will%20help%20them%20if%20the%20need%20arises.%20The%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20evacuation%20from%20any%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%2077%20Indians%20have%20been%20evacuated%2C%20these%20are%20those%20who%20wanted%20to%20return.%20In%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20several%20other%20Indians%20have%20settled%20there%2C%20married%20there%20or%20are%20pursuing%20some%20vocation%20and%20still%20continue%20to%20live%20there.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20return%2C%20we%20will%20facilitate%20their%20return.%20These%2077%20were%20evacuated%20via%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20our%20embassies%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%20coordinated%20very%20closely.%20We%20brought%20them%20by%20road%2C%20after%20which%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Lebanon%20facilitated%20their%20immigration.%20The%20immigration%20at%20the%20border%20was%20long%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20so%20it%20was%20quite%20an%20exercise.%20Then%20we%20took%20care%20of%20their%20boarding%20and%20lodging%2C%20made%20arrangements%20for%20the%20stay.%20Out%20of%20the%2077%2C%2044%20were%20on%20a%20pilgrimage%20to%20various%20sites%20in%20the%20region.%20They%20have%20left%20Beirut%20for%20other%20places%20and%20the%20remaining%2030%20have%20either%20returned%20or%20are%20travelling%20as%20we%20speak%2C%20and%20will%20be%20returning%20to%20India%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%20added%20that%20the%20MEA%20has%20issued%20several%20advisories%20to%20people%20in%20different%20Middle%20Eastern%20countries%20like%20Lebanon%20and%20Israel%20and%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%20However%2C%20they%20do%20not%20need%20to%20be%20evacuated%20as%20of%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20others%20in%20Damascus%20and%20if%20they%20require%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20will%20give%20them%20a%20helping%20hand.%20We%20have%203%2C000%20people%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20about%201%2C000%20people%20in%20UNDOF%20and%20UNIFIL.%20We%20have%20issued%20several%20advisories%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20embassies.%20If%20tomorrow%20there%20is%20any%20need%20for%20evacuation%2C%20we%20will%20do%20that.%20But%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20nothing%20of%20that%20sort%20is%20in%20pipeline.%20In%20Israel%2C%20we%20have%2032%2C000%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20are%20working%20there%20and%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20for%20their%20welfare.%20So%20far%20there%20are%20no%20evacuation%20plans%20from%20any%20other%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyria's%20newly%20appointed%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mohammed%20al-Bashir%2C%20has%20focused%20on%20repatriating%20Syrian%20refugees%20living%20abroad%20as%20one%20of%20his%20key%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Bashir%20aims%20to%20%26quot%3Bbring%20back%20the%20millions%20of%20Syrian%20refugees%20who%20are%20abroad%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20restore%20stability%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Syrian%20government%20continues%20to%20face%20challenges%2C%20including%20unrest%20surrounding%20the%20tomb%20of%20Hafez%20al-Assad%2C%20which%20was%20recently%20set%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734156600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ff4rmp66g_indians-evacuated-from-syria-pti-_625x300_14_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fheard-sounds-of-rockets-bullets-every-day-india