20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPutul%20is%20a%20home-grown%20film%20with%20no%20foreign%20collaboration%2C%20and%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20during%20its%20screening%20in%20a%20mid-sized%20theatre%20was%20purely%20magical.%20Hearing%20praise%20from%20esteemed%20filmmakers%20like%20Aniruddha%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20and%20Margaret%20Zambonini%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Ardenslate%20(a%20script%20development%20company)%2C%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20occasion%2C%20Indira%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20mainstream%20films%20with%20big%20stars%20were%20struggling%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20seven%20Indian%20films%20screened%20at%20Cannes%20brought%20pride%20and%20joy%20to%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20films%20that%20represented%20India%20%E2%80%94%20Indira%20herself%20carried%20her%20culture%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CIndira%20being%20Indira%2C%20honoured%20her%20roots%20and%20culture%20even%20on%20an%20international%20stage%20like%20Cannes.%20She%20began%20her%20speech%20in%20Bangla%20before%20switching%20to%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayan%20fondly%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%E2%80%99s%20poster%20and%20teaser%20were%20also%20launched%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20Sayan%20recounts%20the%20surreal%20moment%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F133350%2Fbhanu-athaiya-unsung-woman-won-indias-1st-oscar-long-ar-rahman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20R%20Rahman%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoted%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20from%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20having%20Rahman%20acknowledge%20a%20film%20you%20have%20worked%20on%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20earned%20international%20accl