the%20village%20where%20farmers%20from%20the%20nearby%20area%20come%20to%20sell%20their%20harvested%20flowers%20twice%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20once%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20once%20in%20the%20evening.%20These%20fresh%20flowers%20are%20dehydrated%20within%2012%20to%2015%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20solar%20dryers%20was%20a%20key%20turning%20point%20in%20Nishad%E2%80%99s%20business%20venture.%20Initially%2C%20he%20dried%20flowers%20in%20an%20open%20environment%2C%20exposed%20to%20dust%2C%20bird%20droppings%2C%20and%20unpredictable%20weather%20conditions%2C%20which%20could%20damage%20the%20product.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20invested%20in%20a%20solar%20dryer%20costing%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20which%20not%20only%20accelerated%20the%20dehydration%20process%20but%20also%20ensured%20that%20the%20product%20remained%20pure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%3A%20A%20game-changer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solar%20dryer%2C%20consisting%20of%20trays%20placed%20on%20a%20metal%20stand%20under%20a%20roof%20of%20polycarbonate%20sheets%20with%20a%20total%20area%20of%20about%20five%20square%20metres%2C%20is%20particularly%20valuable%20during%20the%20monsoon%20when%20flowers%20typically%20get%20wasted.%20With%20this%20setup%2C%20Nishad%20can%20dry%20two%20batches%20of%20flowers%20per%20day%2C%20compared%20to%20just%20one%20using%20open-air%20drying%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325711%2Findore-engineer-foldable-solar-dryers-to-help-farmers-boost-income-tomato-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%20have%20been%20a%20game-changer%20for%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishad.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20ensure%20the%20highest%20quality%20products%20by%20preventing%20dust%2C%20preserving%20colour%20and%20texture%2C%20protecting%20against%20rain%2C%20and%20maintaining%20overall%20product%20quality%2C%20which%20al