ing%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20a%20rockstar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20World%20Down%20Syndrome%20Day%202023%2C%20the%20campaign%20%E2%80%98With%20Us%20Not%20For%20Us%E2%80%99%20featured%20Ultraviolette%20Automotive%E2%80%99s%20video%20about%20Jijo%20to%20show%20what%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20workplace%20looks%20like.%20He%20was%20also%20featured%20in%20%3Cem%3EEnable%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EUK%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESome%20Good%20News%20Australia%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJijo%20is%20expanding%20his%20art%20by%20also%20learning%20music%20along%20with%20Hum-Drum%20Drumming%20Classes%20with%20Rzhude%20David.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20rockstar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20declares%20with%20a%20confident%20smile%2C%20reflecting%20the%20positive%20attitude%20that%20fuels%20his%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202328px)%20100vw%2C%202328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jijo%20poses%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Ultraviolette%20team.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077.jpg%202328w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077-1536x1023.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04972-1_11zon-1733910077-2048x1364.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDSC04