ort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20see%20change%2C%20work%20for%20these%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Prem%20becomes%20somebody%2C%20and%20he%20will%2C%20he%E2%80%99ll%20carry%20this%20goodness%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Naseema%20Khatoon%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733715000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naseema%20Khatoon%2C%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Chaturbhuj%20Sthan%2C%20a%20red-light%20district%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20experienced%20the%20harsh%20stigma%20faced%20by%20sex%20workers%20and%20their%20children%20first-hand.%20Determined%20to%20create%20change%2C%20she%20founded%20Jugnu%20in%202004%2C%20a%20publication%20that%20amplifies%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20marginalised.%20The%20first%20edition%2C%20a%20heartfelt%20four-page%20photocopy%2C%20was%20made%20with%20local%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386658%2Fnaseema-khatoon-jugnu-magazine-muzaffarpur-bihar-empowering-children-of-sex-workers-marginalised-communities%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Do%20Birdwatchers%20Flock%20to%20This%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Sanctuary%20From%20November%20to%20February%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVedanthangal%20Bird%20Sanctuary%20is%20a%20haven%20for%20bird%20lovers%2C%20especially%20from%20November%20to%20March%2C%20when%20migratory%20birds%20flock%20to%20its%20tranquil%20waters.%20This%20period%20is%20considered%20the%20best%20time%20to%20visit%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20as%20it%20comes%20alive%20with%20the%20vibrant%20activity%20of%20hundreds%20of%20av