racts%20with%20it%2C%20they%20go%20back%20home%20and%20call%20their%20mother%2C%20asking%20about%20an%20ingredient%20or%20for%20a%20recipe.%20Something%20they%20used%20to%20have%20as%20a%20child%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dipali%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20entertainment%20or%20sustenance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20identity.%E2%80%9D%20And%20through%20her%20work%2C%20she%20is%20ensuring%20that%20the%20rich%20culinary%20traditions%20of%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20are%20preserved%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dipali%20Khandelwal%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733466538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FDipali-with-Maa_11zon-1733391791.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20preserving%20Rajasthan's%20food%20traditions%2C%20Dipali%20Khandelwal%20is%20documenting%20and%20sharing%20lost%20recipes%2C%20giving%20these%20flavours%20new%20life%20while%20connecting%20generations%20through%20food.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386500%2Fdipali-khandelwal-kindness-meal-rajasthani-dishes-preservation-jaipur-food-heritage%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Couple%20Left%20Corporate%20Careers%20To%20Build%20an%20Organic%20Farming%20Venture%20Generating%20Rs%2090%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20success%2C%20Kotinaga%20Manikanta%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Durga%20Pavani%20took%20a%20bold%20and%20unconventional%20leap.%20Both%20BTech%20graduates%2C%20they%20initially%20followed%20the%20well-trodden%20path%20of%20the%20IT%20industry%20after%20completing%20their%20degrees.%20However%2C%20leaving%20behind%20the%20stability%20and%20rewards%20of%20their%20successful%20careers%2C%20this%20husband-and-wife%20duo%20from%20Guntur%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20traded%20boardrooms%20for%20farm%20fields%2C%20all%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261242%2Fterrace-gardening-tips-youtube-organic-food-diet-thyroid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuit%20of%20healthier%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20better%20world%20for%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManikanta%20worked%20at%20Infosys%2C%20and%20Pavani%20at%20Accenture%2C%20both%20carving%20out%20solid%20careers%20in%20the%20fast-paced%2C%20technology-driven%20world.%20But%20despite%20significant%20success%2C%20they%20felt%20something%20was%20missing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20many%20colleagues%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20struggling%20with%20health%20issues%2C%20despite%20their%20well-paying%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manikanta%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20leading%20sedentary%20lifestyles%2C%20and%20it%20made%20us%20realise%20that%20there%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20their%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pavani.%20This%20realisation%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20contribute%20more%20meaningfully%20to%20society%2C%20planted%20the%20seeds%20for%20%E2%80%98Sreshte%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20store%20for%20all%20organic%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20observed%20the%20growing%20health%20issues%20tied%20to%20poor%20diets%20and%20inactive%20lifestyles%2C%20they%20also%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20organic%20farmers%20in%20securing%20reliable%20markets%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20